1
00:02:07,794 --> 00:02:08,729
Shancai.

2
00:02:09,396 --> 00:02:10,564
Shancai.

3
00:02:11,832 --> 00:02:13,834
-Let me help you with your bag.
-There's no need. Thanks.

4
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:15,836
-It's fine. Let me help you.
-There's no need, Qinghe.

5
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:17,504
Why did you ask me to come out
so suddenly?

6
00:02:17,571 --> 00:02:20,240
I couldn't remember where I put
my swimsuit from last year.

7
00:02:20,307 --> 00:02:21,742
I can only borrow my mom's.

8
00:02:21,808 --> 00:02:24,011
Shancai. Didn't go swimming
the entire summer?

9
00:02:24,077 --> 00:02:25,345
-Yes.
-Obviously.

10
00:02:25,412 --> 00:02:27,547
She's been looking for
Daoming Si's memory the entire summer.

11
00:02:27,614 --> 00:02:28,815
How would she have time to swim?

12
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:30,951
That's right.

13
00:02:31,018 --> 00:02:32,419
Summer is almost over,

14
00:02:32,486 --> 00:02:34,187
so we have to catch
the last few days of summer.

15
00:02:34,254 --> 00:02:35,255
-Yes.
-That's right.

16
00:02:35,322 --> 00:02:37,624
We have to make up
for the entire summer today.

17
00:02:37,691 --> 00:02:39,326
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

18
00:02:54,241 --> 00:02:56,109
Why isn't Shancai here yet?

19
00:02:57,444 --> 00:02:59,112
If I were her, I wouldn't come.

20
00:03:00,213 --> 00:03:01,148
Why?

21
00:03:03,350 --> 00:03:04,918
I'm asking you. Why?

22
00:03:05,285 --> 00:03:06,453
Daoming Si.

23
00:03:08,922 --> 00:03:10,857
Nouveau riche, why are you here?

24
00:03:11,158 --> 00:03:13,427
We're all friends.
Why can't we all go out together?

25
00:03:17,898 --> 00:03:19,700
Hi, Shancai.

26
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,068
Hi.

27
00:03:21,935 --> 00:03:23,904
-Hi, Daoming Si.
-Hi, Daoming Si.

28
00:03:24,137 --> 00:03:25,539
Hi, Princess Yesha.

29
00:03:25,605 --> 00:03:26,773
Hi, Princess Yesha.

30
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,175
Haven't we greeted each other enough?

31
00:03:32,112 --> 00:03:33,280
I'm going inside first.

32
00:03:48,095 --> 00:03:50,564
That's just how he is. He feels awkward
when there are lots of people.

33
00:03:50,630 --> 00:03:51,531
I know.

34
00:03:51,698 --> 00:03:53,233
That's right. You know.

35
00:03:53,700 --> 00:03:55,235
-Let's just have a good time.
-Yes.

36
00:03:57,137 --> 00:03:59,773
It's up to us now.

37
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,475
Yes, Qinghe.

38
00:04:31,171 --> 00:04:32,405
Daoming Si.

39
00:04:32,672 --> 00:04:33,774
What?

40
00:04:34,241 --> 00:04:35,942
It's been a while
since we've been out together.

41
00:04:36,243 --> 00:04:37,644
Do you feel anything special?

42
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:42,549
It feels familiar, right?

43
00:04:43,784 --> 00:04:45,285
It feels familiar. Am I right?

44
00:04:47,087 --> 00:04:48,288
You know,

45
00:04:48,588 --> 00:04:52,959
there's a story behind you, me,
and this swimming pool.

46
00:04:59,599 --> 00:05:04,204
First, you have to imagine that this

47
00:05:05,172 --> 00:05:07,240
is a luxurious yacht.

48
00:05:08,508 --> 00:05:11,211
There's only us F5, Shancai,

49
00:05:11,278 --> 00:05:12,946
and other Yingde classmates.

50
00:05:13,013 --> 00:05:15,415
We dance and eat seafood daily.

51
00:05:15,549 --> 00:05:17,117
We're having so much fun.

52
00:05:17,184 --> 00:05:18,552
Until one night...

53
00:05:18,618 --> 00:05:20,053
Are you done?

54
00:05:20,187 --> 00:05:21,321
Are you mad?

55
00:05:21,755 --> 00:05:23,089
You're right to be mad.

56
00:05:23,323 --> 00:05:25,358
You can kick me into the water. Come on.

57
00:05:25,659 --> 00:05:27,127
Are you this troublesome ever since?

58
00:05:27,194 --> 00:05:29,396
Yes, you can kick me
into the water. Please.

59
00:05:36,436 --> 00:05:37,437
Daoming Si.

60
00:05:37,504 --> 00:05:38,872
Wait for me. I'll race you.

61
00:05:39,172 --> 00:05:40,240
The one who loses is a dog.

62
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:45,979
Qinghe, you can do it.

63
00:05:58,191 --> 00:05:59,459
Why don't you go swimming?

64
00:05:59,526 --> 00:06:00,827
Why don't you go swimming?

65
00:06:01,428 --> 00:06:03,129
I can't swim.

66
00:06:03,964 --> 00:06:05,565
The view is nice here,

67
00:06:05,632 --> 00:06:07,133
so I came out for some air.

68
00:06:07,534 --> 00:06:08,935
Yes, me, too.

69
00:06:14,808 --> 00:06:17,310
What happened between you and Ah Si?

70
00:06:18,945 --> 00:06:19,980
Nothing.

71
00:06:25,218 --> 00:06:26,453
I'm giving you this phone back.

72
00:06:38,198 --> 00:06:39,766
Did it cause you any trouble?

73
00:06:41,368 --> 00:06:42,469
No.

74
00:06:43,937 --> 00:06:45,572
Actually, it's me.

75
00:06:49,075 --> 00:06:50,477
I've decided to give up.

76
00:06:51,278 --> 00:06:52,445
Shancai.

77
00:08:02,482 --> 00:08:04,484
-Qinghe.
-I can't do it anymore.

78
00:08:04,951 --> 00:08:06,086
Don't tell me.

79
00:08:06,219 --> 00:08:07,587
I let Daoming Si win again.

80
00:08:07,754 --> 00:08:09,889
No, Qinghe, you reached the edge first.

81
00:08:09,956 --> 00:08:11,558
You won big-time.

82
00:08:11,624 --> 00:08:12,492
