87
00:08:21,134 --> 00:08:23,436
-Yes!
-Qinghe, you're so great.

88
00:08:24,237 --> 00:08:25,505
Mimi.

89
00:08:25,572 --> 00:08:27,741
You don't have
to blindly admire me so much.

90
00:08:27,941 --> 00:08:30,010
Though I know
my swimming skills are great,

91
00:08:31,011 --> 00:08:33,246
it's Daoming Si that's too lousy.

92
00:08:34,114 --> 00:08:35,248
Where's Daoming Si?

93
00:08:35,782 --> 00:08:37,017
Where's Daoming Si?

94
00:08:37,984 --> 00:08:39,652
