95
00:08:39,719 --> 00:08:41,321
Help!

96
00:08:43,423 --> 00:08:44,791
I was even thinking

97
00:08:45,525 --> 00:08:47,594
that Daoming Si might have gained
his memory back.

98
00:08:48,228 --> 00:08:50,997
However, he realized
that you're the one he loves.

99
00:08:51,798 --> 00:08:53,733
So he'd rather not have his past.

100
00:08:56,536 --> 00:08:57,904
If that's really the case,

101
00:08:58,505 --> 00:09:00,306
then, to him, isn't my persistence

102
00:09:00,673 --> 00:09:02,242
too selfish?

103
00:09:03,343 --> 00:09:04,844
That's why I should give up.

104
00:09:07,213 --> 00:09:08,648
You can't give up.

105
00:09:11,017 --> 00:09:13,253
You're not someone who just gives up.

106
00:09:16,356 --> 00:09:17,390
Yesha.

107
00:09:18,158 --> 00:09:19,392
I'm really tired.

108
00:09:20,026 --> 00:09:21,227
I don't have any strength anymore.

109
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,665
Just hold on a little more.

110
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,802
If you're not beside him,

111
00:09:29,135 --> 00:09:30,670
when I leave...

112
00:09:31,104 --> 00:09:33,473
Help!

113
00:09:33,740 --> 00:09:36,276
Daoming Si, he...

114
00:09:36,743 --> 00:09:38,278
He...

115
00:09:46,252 --> 00:09:47,520
Ah Xing.

116
00:09:47,587 --> 00:09:48,888
Daoming Si.

117
00:09:49,522 --> 00:09:50,690
Daoming Si.

118
00:10:14,781 --> 00:10:17,317
Qinghe, will Daoming Si die?

119
00:10:17,383 --> 00:10:18,885
Stop talking nonsense.

120
00:10:22,856 --> 00:10:24,691
Ah Xing, wake up.

121
00:10:24,991 --> 00:10:26,793
I don't want to see you this way.

122
00:10:26,926 --> 00:10:27,861
Ah Xing.

123
00:10:54,988 --> 00:10:56,222
Daoming Si.

124
00:10:56,456 --> 00:10:58,424
-Daoming Si.
-Ah Xing.

125
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:02,061
Ah Xing.

126
00:11:02,295 --> 00:11:03,630
Daoming Si.

127
00:11:04,964 --> 00:11:06,499
Daoming Si.

128
00:11:06,566 --> 00:11:08,701
Ah Xing.

129
00:11:09,402 --> 00:11:11,771
SURGERY ONGOING

130
00:11:31,991 --> 00:11:34,160
It turns out that life is so fragile.

131
00:11:35,962 --> 00:11:38,097
Ah Xing is so fragile, too.

132
00:11:42,902 --> 00:11:44,404
Maybe I'm not the one leaving.

133
00:11:46,739 --> 00:11:49,709
Maybe he'll leave first.

134
00:11:55,348 --> 00:11:58,718
Life can be gone in just
a blink of an eye.

135
00:12:01,020 --> 00:12:02,455
Same goes for Ah Xing.

136
00:12:03,556 --> 00:12:05,925
He might be gone in a blink of an eye.

137
00:12:07,227 --> 00:12:08,494
He won't.

138
00:12:09,362 --> 00:12:10,430
You know,

139
00:12:10,797 --> 00:12:12,732
Daoming Si's body is amazing.

140
00:12:13,132 --> 00:12:15,602
His ability to recover
is like that of a dog.

141
00:12:16,436 --> 00:12:18,104
When I mentioned
that he's like a dog before,

142
00:12:18,171 --> 00:12:19,872
F3 laughed so hard.

143
00:12:20,773 --> 00:12:22,508
Daoming Si was so furious.

144
00:12:24,077 --> 00:12:25,845
But he's really like a dog.

145
00:12:26,379 --> 00:12:27,747
He'll recover soon.

146
00:12:28,181 --> 00:12:29,616
So don't worry.

147
00:12:29,816 --> 00:12:31,317
Just focus on praying for him.

148
00:12:43,763 --> 00:12:45,164
Let's pray together.

149
00:12:45,231 --> 00:12:46,399
Okay.

150
00:12:50,837 --> 00:12:51,871
God.

151
00:12:53,339 --> 00:12:55,275
Please give me one more chance.

152
00:12:56,242 --> 00:12:58,278
Please also give Ah Xing one more chance.

153
00:13:09,889 --> 00:13:11,190
Where is Ah Si?

154
00:13:17,864 --> 00:13:19,265
He's still being operated on.

155
00:13:25,805 --> 00:13:27,407
Was this your idea?

156
00:13:29,375 --> 00:13:31,811
How many times do you have to endanger
Ah Si before you're satisfied?

157
00:13:32,145 --> 00:13:34,681
This was my idea, not Shancai's.

158
00:13:35,081 --> 00:13:36,549
Please don't cause her any trouble.

159
00:13:38,117 --> 00:13:40,353
You colluded so many times
to force Ah Si to do what you want.

160
00:13:41,087 --> 00:13:43,356
Can't you see he's had enough?

161
00:13:45,158 --> 00:13:46,359
Dong Shancai.

162
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:48,127
Chen Qinghe.

163
00:13:49,829 --> 00:13:51,864
If anything happens to Ah Si,

164
00:13:53,333 --> 00:13:55,301
I'll let you know the consequences.

165
00:13:59,439 --> 00:14:02,041
SURGERY ONGOING

166
00:14:08,114 --> 00:14:09,082
Doctor.

167
00:14:09,349 --> 00:14:10,717
He's out of danger.

168
00:14:11,184 --> 00:14:13,419
However, the patient is still unconscious.

169
00:14:28,901 --> 00:14:31,904
It's confirmed that the blood clot
in his brain has already dissipated.

170
00:14:32,638 --> 00:14:35,341
However, whether the severe shock
he suffered this time

171
00:14:35,541 --> 00:14:37,143
would be beneficial
to regaining his memory

172
00:14:37,276 --> 00:14:39,112
or not,

173
00:14:39,545 --> 00:14:41,881
we'll only find out when he wakes up.

174
00:14:44,317 --> 00:14:45,351
Thank you.

175
00:14:45,518 --> 00:14:46,619
You're welcome.

176
00:14:56,529 --> 00:14:58,498
<i>Regardless of who he has in his memories,</i>

177
00:14:58,865 --> 00:15:00,433
<i>only Yesha would exist</i>

178
00:15:00,933 --> 00:15:02,902
<i>in his life in the future.</i>

179
00:15:17,383 --> 00:15:18,518
<i>Ah Xing.</i>

180
00:15:20,186 --> 00:15:21,821
<i>Can you please wake up?</i>

181
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:26,426
<i>I have something really important
to tell you.</i>

182
00:15:47,547 --> 00:15:49,649
Why won't you tell the truth?

183
00:15:50,683 --> 00:15:52,018
What do you mean?

184
00:15:52,785 --> 00:15:54,320
You love Ah Si.

185
00:15:57,323 --> 00:15:58,658
You love him,

186
00:15:59,192 --> 00:16:00,993
but why are you pretending you don't?

187
00:16:02,695 --> 00:16:03,963
Because of Shancai?

188
00:16:09,469 --> 00:16:11,671
I also felt sorry for Shancai before.

189
00:16:12,805 --> 00:16:13,673
However,

190
00:16:15,608 --> 00:16:17,643
don't you feel sorry for Ah Si

191
00:16:18,811 --> 00:16:20,680
in forcing him to go back to Shancai?

192
00:16:23,182 --> 00:16:26,185
Bravely loving him is not selfish,

193
00:16:27,286 --> 00:16:29,188
yet pushing him away is senseless.

194
00:16:30,723 --> 00:16:32,091
You're relying on your youth

195
00:16:33,025 --> 00:16:35,061
and your limitless future

196
00:16:35,962 --> 00:16:37,163
to sacrifice

197
00:16:37,864 --> 00:16:39,565
and betray your own feelings.

198
00:16:40,766 --> 00:16:42,935
You think that's the highest form of love.

199
00:16:45,004 --> 00:16:45,905
Now,

200
00:16:46,906 --> 00:16:48,207
you should know

201
00:16:50,476 --> 00:16:52,211
that tomorrow might not come.

202
00:16:54,247 --> 00:16:55,214
However,

203
00:16:55,982 --> 00:16:57,950
the words you can't say today

204
00:16:59,752 --> 00:17:01,787
might become your regret in the future.

205
00:17:05,057 --> 00:17:06,092
Yesha.

206
00:17:08,794 --> 00:17:10,463
I only have one son.

207
00:17:12,031 --> 00:17:13,666
Stop tormenting him.

208
00:17:16,335 --> 00:17:17,603
I'm begging you.

209
00:17:20,406 --> 00:17:21,908
Please treasure him.

210
00:17:31,684 --> 00:17:33,252
Think about it carefully.

211
00:18:19,599 --> 00:18:21,934
Stop. Stop beating him up.

212
00:18:22,001 --> 00:18:23,803
Stop hitting him.

213
00:18:24,170 --> 00:18:25,471
I really like you.

214
00:18:26,839 --> 00:18:28,608
Wait, don't do this.

215
00:18:31,744 --> 00:18:33,713
Have you ever really liked me?

216
00:18:40,386 --> 00:18:42,555
Actually, I've never really liked you.

217
00:18:43,856 --> 00:18:45,625
If I did,

218
00:18:46,025 --> 00:18:47,727
I won't just leave right now.

219
00:18:48,661 --> 00:18:49,729
Yesha.

220
00:18:51,964 --> 00:18:53,099
Daoming Si.

221
00:18:57,603 --> 00:18:59,739
Shancai.

222
00:19:00,339 --> 00:19:01,574
Shancai.

223
00:19:02,241 --> 00:19:03,376
<i>Shancai.</i>

224
00:19:04,276 --> 00:19:05,544
<i>Shancai.</i>

225
00:19:06,545 --> 00:19:07,947
<i>Shancai.</i>

226
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:14,286
<i>Shancai.</i>

227
00:19:15,221 --> 00:19:18,891
<i>Shancai.</i>

228
00:19:33,339 --> 00:19:35,541
Ah Xing, you're awake.

229
00:19:38,944 --> 00:19:40,846
Shancai, Ah Xing is awake.

230
00:19:45,351 --> 00:19:46,952
Congratulations, Daoming Si.

231
00:19:48,287 --> 00:19:49,755
Do you want some water?

232
00:19:50,122 --> 00:19:51,557
Or do you want to eat something?

233
00:19:51,724 --> 00:19:53,159
-Or...
-No, I don't want anything.

234
00:19:53,225 --> 00:19:55,027
Go out first. Let me be alone, okay?

235
00:20:56,756 --> 00:20:57,723
Shancai.

236
00:20:58,357 --> 00:20:59,658
I have something to tell you.

237
00:21:00,893 --> 00:21:01,827
Go ahead.

238
00:21:06,899 --> 00:21:08,067
Another day, maybe.

239
00:21:08,801 --> 00:21:10,336
Okay, that's fine, too.

240
00:21:10,402 --> 00:21:11,871
You've taken care of him the whole night.

241
00:21:11,937 --> 00:21:13,773
You look so pale.

242
00:21:14,106 --> 00:21:15,741
Since Daoming Si is awake,

243
00:21:15,975 --> 00:21:17,243
you should go home and rest first.

244
00:21:18,244 --> 00:21:19,411
There's no need.

245
00:21:20,079 --> 00:21:22,448
They'll come over tomorrow anyway.
Don't worry.

246
00:21:24,183 --> 00:21:25,217
Come on.

247
00:21:25,951 --> 00:21:27,386
Rest first then come back.

248
00:21:27,453 --> 00:21:28,888
Daoming Si needs to rest, too.

249
00:21:33,159 --> 00:21:34,260
All right.

250
00:21:34,827 --> 00:21:35,995
I'll go ahead.

251
00:21:36,061 --> 00:21:37,263
Stop worrying.

252
00:21:37,329 --> 00:21:38,564
I'll be back soon.

253
00:21:38,631 --> 00:21:39,732
See you later.

254
00:21:41,033 --> 00:21:42,401
Bye.

255
00:22:45,130 --> 00:22:46,265
Is he asleep?

256
00:22:47,032 --> 00:22:50,102
Why didn't you make a sound?
You scared me.

257
00:22:50,236 --> 00:22:51,503
You're even blaming us.

258
00:22:51,570 --> 00:22:52,838
We were standing here for a while.

259
00:22:52,905 --> 00:22:54,740
You were just standing there
and not moving at all.

260
00:22:56,308 --> 00:22:57,610
Yesha said Ah Si is awake.

261
00:22:58,277 --> 00:22:59,178
Did you see Yesha?

262
00:22:59,245 --> 00:23:00,613
We saw her by the elevator earlier.

263
00:23:01,313 --> 00:23:03,249
The doctor said he'd be fine
when he wakes up.

264
00:23:03,315 --> 00:23:04,583
However, he's resting now.

265
00:23:04,650 --> 00:23:06,151
He said he wants to be alone.

266
00:23:08,120 --> 00:23:09,555
This guy.

267
00:23:10,055 --> 00:23:12,258
He periodically gets into trouble
and lets us worry about him.

268
00:23:12,324 --> 00:23:14,059
Now, he wants to be alone.

269
00:23:14,460 --> 00:23:16,462
There's nothing we can do.
He's the patient.

270
00:23:16,962 --> 00:23:20,432
