wait for Young Master Daoming Si's orders.

271
00:23:23,869 --> 00:23:26,805
Meizuo, let's buy some fruits
nearby first.

272
00:23:28,007 --> 00:23:29,074
All right.

273
00:23:29,275 --> 00:23:32,678
Lei, we'll leave Young Master
Daoming Si to you.

274
00:23:32,778 --> 00:23:34,480
-See you later.
-Bye.

275
00:24:05,978 --> 00:24:06,845
How are you?

276
00:24:09,815 --> 00:24:11,116
Qinghe contacted us.

277
00:24:12,885 --> 00:24:14,186
It seems he's blaming himself.

278
00:24:17,389 --> 00:24:20,025
This is the first time he talked
so clearly.

279
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:26,732
Good thing he's awake.

280
00:24:29,234 --> 00:24:30,769
Based on Ah Si's swimming skills,

281
00:24:34,106 --> 00:24:35,474
how could he drown?

282
00:24:37,409 --> 00:24:40,946
Maybe it's because he's not
in a good mood recently.

283
00:24:42,348 --> 00:24:43,415
Why?

284
00:24:45,017 --> 00:24:46,185
I don't know.

285
00:24:46,852 --> 00:24:48,120
It seems he...

286
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,926
Never mind. Yesha's with him anyway.

287
00:24:54,126 --> 00:24:55,761
He'll recover soon.

288
00:25:03,969 --> 00:25:05,504
I really want to go on a vacation.

289
00:25:08,474 --> 00:25:11,243
The industrious Shancai
wants to go on a vacation?

290
00:25:13,946 --> 00:25:15,748
Summer is almost over.

291
00:25:16,315 --> 00:25:19,551
The beach would soon become lonely.

292
00:25:31,530 --> 00:25:32,664
Wait a moment.

293
00:26:02,261 --> 00:26:03,595
What kind of sea do you want?

294
00:26:08,233 --> 00:26:11,437
I want waves on the ocean.

295
00:26:12,438 --> 00:26:15,974
The slow and gentle kind.

296
00:26:17,810 --> 00:26:18,877
How about the sun?

297
00:26:20,879 --> 00:26:24,650
The sun? It's best if it's almost setting.

298
00:26:31,523 --> 00:26:32,458
Done.

299
00:26:35,961 --> 00:26:37,129
Sign it.

300
00:26:37,563 --> 00:26:38,497
Okay.

301
00:26:53,946 --> 00:26:55,080
Thank you.

302
00:27:02,754 --> 00:27:04,690
Can I ask for a favor?

303
00:27:11,296 --> 00:27:13,098
Can you go with me to eat something?

304
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,034
Okay.

305
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:23,542
<i>Ah Si almost died.</i>

306
00:27:24,309 --> 00:27:30,249
He almost disappeared
from this world before me.

307
00:27:34,786 --> 00:27:41,093
Good thing God, Buddha,
and Allah protected him.

308
00:27:42,427 --> 00:27:44,863
Why are you thanking God and Allah?

309
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:46,331
Sha.

310
00:27:47,065 --> 00:27:49,568
Why can't I love Ah Xing properly?

311
00:27:51,036 --> 00:27:52,271
You're asking me?

312
00:27:52,905 --> 00:27:54,373
I want to ask you.

313
00:27:54,907 --> 00:27:56,742
Am I too sleepy?

314
00:27:57,176 --> 00:28:00,145
I can't think of a reason
why I can't love him properly.

315
00:28:01,947 --> 00:28:03,448
Why?

316
00:28:06,351 --> 00:28:10,389
Maybe God is jealous of Ah Xing.

317
00:28:10,455 --> 00:28:13,125
He's reluctant to let
such a cute angel like you

318
00:28:13,258 --> 00:28:15,027
stay beside him.

319
00:28:49,061 --> 00:28:50,929
What time is it? How long have I slept?

320
00:28:50,996 --> 00:28:52,564
You just lied down for five minutes.

321
00:28:52,631 --> 00:28:55,934
That's impossible. I must have slept for a
long time. That's why I'm so energetic.

322
00:28:56,001 --> 00:28:58,870
-No, you didn't.
-I'm going to the hospital.

323
00:28:58,937 --> 00:29:01,039
You can't go to the hospital.
You haven't even slept.

324
00:29:01,106 --> 00:29:03,875
I'm very energetic. I can even run
a marathon. I'm going to the hospital.

325
00:29:03,942 --> 00:29:06,511
-You can't.
-I'm going to visit Ah Xing now.

326
00:29:06,578 --> 00:29:08,146
-You can't.
-I have to go.

327
00:29:08,213 --> 00:29:10,115
-I said you can't.
-I'm going there now.

328
00:29:10,182 --> 00:29:12,484
I'm telling him I love him. Let go.

329
00:29:16,121 --> 00:29:17,222
Move.

330
00:29:22,561 --> 00:29:24,763
You're so funny.

331
00:29:42,814 --> 00:29:43,982
That door is open.

332
00:29:44,082 --> 00:29:45,350
He doesn't want to be alone anymore?

333
00:29:47,386 --> 00:29:48,487
Ah Xing's gone.

334
00:29:48,553 --> 00:29:49,588
What?

335
00:29:52,624 --> 00:29:54,026
Yesha.

336
00:30:00,732 --> 00:30:03,101
<i>She looked as silly as you
when she was standing</i>

337
00:30:06,371 --> 00:30:07,839
<i>under the La Sagrada Familia.</i>

338
00:30:10,208 --> 00:30:11,643
<i>It's a cute kind of silliness.</i>

339
00:30:13,211 --> 00:30:15,614
<i>You wouldn't resist calling her stupid.</i>

340
00:30:17,149 --> 00:30:18,483
<i>She got mad, of course.</i>

341
00:30:19,685 --> 00:30:20,886
<i>She turned her head</i>

342
00:30:22,454 --> 00:30:24,456
<i>and her long hair flipped in the wind.</i>

343
00:30:26,224 --> 00:30:27,826
<i>She smelled like baby powder.</i>

344
00:30:28,994 --> 00:30:30,329
<i>She's different.</i>

345
00:30:30,662 --> 00:30:32,164
<i>She's like the sun.</i>

346
00:30:33,699 --> 00:30:35,734
<i>When she lifted her head
to look at the stars,</i>

347
00:30:37,035 --> 00:30:38,704
<i>she also lit up with them.</i>

348
00:30:40,305 --> 00:30:41,640
<i>That's Yesha.</i>

349
00:30:43,108 --> 00:30:44,543
<i>And that's Shancai.</i>

350
00:30:46,244 --> 00:30:47,746
<i>There's a Shancai.</i>

351
00:30:49,481 --> 00:30:52,551
<i>When I woke up, there's also a Yesha.</i>

352
00:30:54,119 --> 00:30:56,088
<i>What a big joke.</i>

353
00:30:58,724 --> 00:31:00,225
<i>You're also laughing at me.</i>

354
00:31:02,828 --> 00:31:05,530
<i>Stop denying it. I heard you.</i>

355
00:31:06,898 --> 00:31:08,166
<i>I don't blame you.</i>

356
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:12,204
<i>If I were you, I would laugh, too.</i>

357
00:31:14,773 --> 00:31:16,241
<i>It's a shame that I'm not you.</i>

358
00:31:17,442 --> 00:31:21,713
<i>That's why I want to cry.</i>

359
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,399
Miss, are you looking for someone?

360
00:31:42,634 --> 00:31:44,703
I don't know where he has gone to.

361
00:31:51,777 --> 00:31:53,278
I'll go report it.

362
00:33:37,482 --> 00:33:40,852
Ah Xing.

363
00:33:42,387 --> 00:33:43,588
Ah Xing.

364
00:33:45,690 --> 00:33:47,259
Ah Xing, you fool.

365
00:33:47,325 --> 00:33:49,227
You're ridiculous, you...

366
00:34:25,830 --> 00:34:26,798
Yesha.

367
00:34:28,066 --> 00:34:29,534
I thought you left.

368
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:32,704
I left?

369
00:34:34,005 --> 00:34:35,006
Why?

370
00:34:38,109 --> 00:34:40,278
Because you always say
you can't go back anymore.

371
00:34:40,845 --> 00:34:42,280
And you also don't want to go back.

372
00:34:43,915 --> 00:34:44,950
However...

373
00:34:45,483 --> 00:34:47,652
I still keep pushing you back to Shancai.

374
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,121
Ah Xing.

375
00:34:52,023 --> 00:34:53,458
I messed up

376
00:34:53,792 --> 00:34:55,727
everything, right?

377
00:35:02,901 --> 00:35:04,569
There's something I want to tell you.

378
00:35:05,203 --> 00:35:07,472
-I have something to tell you, too.
-I want to tell you first...

379
00:35:07,539 --> 00:35:08,440
I love you.

380
00:35:14,279 --> 00:35:16,548
Originally, I wanted to just keep that
inside of me.

381
00:35:17,782 --> 00:35:19,484
And never say it out loud.

382
00:35:23,321 --> 00:35:24,956
Until that day at the swimming pool.

383
00:35:25,023 --> 00:35:27,926
When I saved you, I realized

384
00:35:30,095 --> 00:35:31,863
that if you're not by my side

385
00:35:32,497 --> 00:35:33,865
and I'm just living alone,

386
00:35:35,967 --> 00:35:37,302
I'd rather die.

387
00:35:37,969 --> 00:35:39,671
What are you talking about?

388
00:35:40,939 --> 00:35:43,775
Yes, I'm talking nonsense.

389
00:35:44,209 --> 00:35:45,644
I'm crazy.

390
00:35:47,212 --> 00:35:48,613
I love you,

391
00:35:50,815 --> 00:35:53,618
but I did so many things I regret.

392
00:35:58,923 --> 00:36:01,893
I'm stupid and silly

393
00:36:03,395 --> 00:36:04,996
and really infuriating, right?

394
00:36:08,700 --> 00:36:10,435
However, you once said

395
00:36:11,269 --> 00:36:13,104
that you like my silliness.

396
00:36:17,609 --> 00:36:21,980
You also told me that
no matter who you are,

397
00:36:22,747 --> 00:36:24,382
you'd always like me.

398
00:36:25,483 --> 00:36:26,685
Do you remember that?

399
00:36:30,789 --> 00:36:31,890
I do.

400
00:36:34,793 --> 00:36:36,494
I remember everything

401
00:36:37,696 --> 00:36:39,164
that I've said

402
00:36:40,632 --> 00:36:42,033
and done.

403
00:36:46,204 --> 00:36:47,305
It won't happen again.

404
00:36:47,639 --> 00:36:49,140
I won't leave you again.

405
00:36:52,043 --> 00:36:54,045
Regardless if you're Ah Xing or Ah Si,

406
00:36:56,247 --> 00:36:58,083
I won't force you
to recover your memories.

407
00:36:59,284 --> 00:37:01,152
And I won't force you
to love another person.

408
00:37:02,987 --> 00:37:05,356
Because I've had enough being jealous.

409
00:37:06,624 --> 00:37:09,494
I don't want to feel that anymore.

410
00:37:20,305 --> 00:37:22,107
I'm done with what I want to say.

411
00:37:23,374 --> 00:37:24,743
What do you want to tell me?

412
00:37:28,246 --> 00:37:30,081
The rain is getting stronger.

413
00:37:46,131 --> 00:37:47,599
Let's go home.

414
00:37:50,135 --> 00:37:51,970
That's what you wanted to tell me?

415
00:39:09,414 --> 00:39:10,682
Daoming Si.

416
00:39:13,785 --> 00:39:15,220
<i>Today, I finally know</i>

417
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:18,089
that you've really
completely forgotten me.

418
00:39:19,691 --> 00:39:21,059
You've really forgotten.

419
00:39:21,726 --> 00:39:23,394
<i>Regardless how many memories
we have together,</i>

420
00:39:24,329 --> 00:39:25,864
<i>the one I love is Yesha.</i>

421
00:39:53,124 --> 00:39:57,562
HUAZE LEI
CALLING

422
00:42:05,823 --> 00:42:07,058
Good morning, Sha.

423
00:42:17,735 --> 00:42:19,137
You're awake?

424
00:42:20,338 --> 00:42:21,739
You're making breakfast?

425
00:42:23,908 --> 00:42:25,576
How rare.

426
00:42:26,577 --> 00:42:28,212
Go away.

427
00:42:31,516 --> 00:42:33,418
You're happy, right?

428
00:42:34,552 --> 00:42:35,453
Right?

429
00:42:36,988 --> 00:42:38,089
Right?

430
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:40,258
Go away.

431
00:42:44,395 --> 00:42:45,563
Drink this.

432
00:42:49,333 --> 00:42:50,868
Last night,

433
00:42:55,073 --> 00:42:57,708
Ah Xing must have said something
to you, right?

434
00:42:58,209 --> 00:42:59,177
No.

435
00:42:59,811 --> 00:43:01,312
-No?
-No.

436
00:43:05,349 --> 00:43:06,584
All right.

437
00:43:08,686 --> 00:43:09,620
I'm sure he...

438
00:43:11,889 --> 00:43:13,091
He didn't.

439
00:43:13,224 --> 00:43:14,425
No?

440
00:43:15,093 --> 00:43:16,894
Cut it out.

441
00:43:17,862 --> 00:43:19,297
Do you really think

442
00:43:20,765 --> 00:43:23,701
I couldn't feel that you've changed?

443
00:43:24,802 --> 00:43:26,871
And Ah Xing loves you so much.

444
00:43:28,106 --> 00:43:29,507
Then he saw you

445
00:43:30,241 --> 00:43:33,611
searching for him in the rain.

446
00:43:33,678 --> 00:43:35,179
And he was so moved.

447
00:43:35,246 --> 00:43:36,848
So he...

448
00:43:36,914 --> 00:43:38,316
I was the one who kissed him.

449
00:43:39,016 --> 00:43:39,984
Really?

450
00:43:40,418 --> 00:43:42,220
I even told him I love him.

451
00:43:50,361 --> 00:43:51,596
-Sha.
-Yes.

452
00:43:52,063 --> 00:43:54,098
I think I didn't have the courage before.

453
00:43:55,099 --> 00:43:56,968
However, now I know

454
00:43:57,502 --> 00:43:59,871
that the person who doesn't have
the right to talk about the future

455
00:43:59,937 --> 00:44:02,039
is the one who doesn't know
how to hold on to today.

456
00:44:04,408 --> 00:44:05,877
From now on,

457
00:44:06,210 --> 00:44:09,347
I want Ah Si and me to have
no regrets every day.

458
00:44:23,361 --> 00:44:24,529
Oh, no.

459
00:44:25,163 --> 00:44:27,832
Well... We have to hurry.

460
00:44:28,399 --> 00:44:31,235
I gave you that... ring before.

461
00:44:31,335 --> 00:44:33,538
Do you remember? Where did you put it?

462
00:44:33,871 --> 00:44:37,341
Go to your room. Hurry.

463
00:44:37,408 --> 00:44:39,343
-Help me find it.
-What are you looking for?

464
00:44:39,410 --> 00:44:42,380
The meteor ring I brought back
from Spain last time.

465
00:44:42,446 --> 00:44:45,183
The one you took away.
Help me find it. Please.

466
00:44:46,884 --> 00:44:47,985
Where did it go?

467
00:44:48,686 --> 00:44:51,989
Miss, my goodness.
Your things are so disorganized.

468
00:44:52,523 --> 00:44:53,824
This one?

469
00:44:54,792 --> 00:44:56,160
<i>Amitabha</i>.

470
00:44:56,427 --> 00:44:59,397
Good thing it's still here.
I'll go take care of this then.

471
00:44:59,497 --> 00:45:00,765
Take care of it?

472
00:45:01,332 --> 00:45:02,400
You forgot.

473
00:45:02,900 --> 00:45:04,869
I told you this ring is cursed.

474
00:45:04,936 --> 00:45:07,972
You and Ah Xing have a good future now.

475
00:45:08,039 --> 00:45:11,742
How can you keep such a scary thing
with you and bring you bad luck?

476
00:45:11,842 --> 00:45:15,012
Sha, why are you so superstitious?

477
00:45:15,913 --> 00:45:18,015
Being superstitious is better
than you having bad luck.

478
00:45:18,082 --> 00:45:21,219
If I can take you and Ah Xing
into church earlier

479
00:45:21,285 --> 00:45:23,154
to say, "I do,"

480
00:45:23,221 --> 00:45:26,657
I'll even drink Taoist holy water.

481
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,728
Don't drink that first.

482
00:45:31,429 --> 00:45:32,630
Let me make a phone call.

483
00:45:32,964 --> 00:45:34,232
Who are you going to call?

484
00:45:42,740 --> 00:45:43,941
Who?

485
00:45:46,844 --> 00:45:47,812
Hello.

486
00:47:23,307 --> 00:47:25,309
Subtitle translated by Coleen Chua
